Ando [[Slovaiko]] beshen but [[roma]] (prinjaren pen 1.6% andar sa le manusha le Slovaikosko, pale chaches shai te aven 5.6% vai buteder).

Kathe shirden (astaren) te inklen romane shkole kai siklyaren pen i [[romani ćhib]] vi o [[romanipen]], o romano sanskrtipen thai puranipen. Kadya si i romani [[Gandhiskri shkola (Zvolenostar)]] ([[2004]] bershestar). Vi ande aver mashkarutne shkole andar [[Bratislava]] thai [[Koshice]] siklyaren pen i [[romani ćhib]] vi o [[romanipen]] sar ek kotor andar lengo siklyaripnasko programo.

